         <div type="edition">
            <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1" xml:id="Prologue1">
               <label>First prologue</label>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <ab>
                     በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ሥሉስ፡ ዘኢይሰድቅ፡ ዋሕድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> 
                     ለዘከመዝ፡ እግዚእ፡ እንዘ፡ እገኒ፡ ወእሰግድ፡ እነግር፡ ዜና፡
                  </ab>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <ab>
                     ይከውን፡ ፈጻሜ፡ ኀይለ፡ ቃል፡ በአስተታልዎ። በሰላመ፡ ዚአሁ፡ አሜን።
                  </ab>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="2" xml:id="Prologue2">
               <label>Second prologue</label>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <ab>
                     አቀድም፡ አእኵቶቶ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ በእንተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ዘውእቱ፡ ወልዱ፡
                  </ab>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <ab>
                     ደናግል፡ ወመናኮሳት፡ እስመ፡ ውእቱኒ፡ ኢሐፀ፡ እምኔሆሙ። ጸሎቱ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> አሜን።
                  </ab>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="3" xml:id="MainPart">
               <label>Main part</label>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <ab>
                     ወሀለወት፡ አሐቲ፡ ሀገር፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ተሰመይ፡ ሮሐ፡
                  </ab>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <ab>
                     በጽላሎተ፡ ክነፊሁ፡ እንዘ፡ ይከድነነ፡ ወኀበ፡ ረፈቀ፡ ያርፍቀነ። <gap reason="omitted"/> አሜን።
                  </ab>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
